## Install Tailscale 
sudo curl -fsSL https://tailscale.com/install.sh | sh

## Start Tailscale
sudo tailscale up

## If you want to enable ssh access from the Tailscale web management 
sudo tailscale up -ssh

## Authenticate the server
go to https://login.tailscale.com/a/<14 digit hexidecimal number>
e.g. https://login.tailscale.com/a/1520e49f019277

Log into your tailscale account

There will be an option to "Conect" the device to tailnet - select "Connect"

The new device will be added to you account and can be seen under "Machines" in the Tailscale web UI
